com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.login

Interface LoginSupportFeatures


  • public interface LoginSupportFeatures
    Set of features provider of the login refresh message supports. This is additional information sent between components.
    See Also:
    LoginRefresh, LoginSupportFeaturesFlags
